{"entity":{"id":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","type":"chapter","slug":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","label":"Hos.8","rawId":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","book":{"id":"rect9laYKg0Xd0Uzg","type":"book","slug":"hos","label":"Hosea","subtitle":"Minor Prophets","count":197,"description":"14 chapters, 95 people, 44 places"}},"stats":{"verses":14,"people":2,"places":3,"events":1},"nodes":[{"id":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Hos.8","slug":"hos_8","score":14},{"id":"rect9laYKg0Xd0Uzg","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Hosea","slug":"hos","score":197},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":4},{"id":"recEtv9ql7Hh4XAW4","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Ephraim","slug":"ephraim_1206","score":2},{"id":"recEP3QZ3HUmIkv4Q","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Samaria","slug":"samaria_1022","score":2},{"id":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Assyria","slug":"assyria_111","score":1},{"id":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Egypt","slug":"egypt_362","score":1},{"id":"recekTocE5mIkvDEk","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Prophecies of Hosea","slug":"event-206","score":14}],"links":[{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"rect9laYKg0Xd0Uzg","label":"part of"},{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"recEtv9ql7Hh4XAW4","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"recEP3QZ3HUmIkv4Q","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rechrbgu4D2H0U6OS","target":"recekTocE5mIkvDEk","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recYHdA3cwJtYMQfJ","ref":"Hos.8.1","text":"Set the trumpet to thy mouth. He shall come as an eagle against the house of the LORD, because they have transgressed my covenant, and trespassed against my law.","year":-780},{"id":"recQqwC6Ft9xF8RlY","ref":"Hos.8.2","text":"Israel shall cry unto me, My God, we know thee.","year":-780},{"id":"recP3RGYFoEdAeIJh","ref":"Hos.8.3","text":"Israel hath cast off the thing that is good: the enemy shall pursue him.","year":-780},{"id":"recPVeuCweQ7yNJ1I","ref":"Hos.8.4","text":"They have set up kings, but not by me: they have made princes, and I knew it not: of their silver and their gold have they made them idols, that they may be cut off.","year":-780},{"id":"recXxQG42OW7rIzBx","ref":"Hos.8.5","text":"Thy calf, O Samaria, hath cast thee off; mine anger is kindled against them: how long will it be ere they attain to innocency?","year":-780},{"id":"recjzqdwtnex2dHcu","ref":"Hos.8.6","text":"For from Israel was it also: the workman made it; therefore it is not God: but the calf of Samaria shall be broken in pieces.","year":-780},{"id":"recpNJtUSGi2xUfpv","ref":"Hos.8.7","text":"For they have sown the wind, and they shall reap the whirlwind: it hath no stalk: the bud shall yield no meal: if so be it yield, the strangers shall swallow it up.","year":-780},{"id":"receZPP6lcxFhoQ0M","ref":"Hos.8.8","text":"Israel is swallowed up: now shall they be among the Gentiles as a vessel wherein is no pleasure.","year":-780}]}
